Class Dialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • photos.util.Dialog

  • public class Dialog
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Mihir Patel, Maxim Torubarov Utility class used for creating Alert boxes based on AlertType and the message to be displayed in the Alert Box and returns them, so we can do different things with them on the receiving end like showandwait() or just show().
